reviewText: OMG come on IDK why the graded tests of this course are so bad. Those tests are just time-consuming; they force you to do a lot of thing not relating to Encapsulation at all. Taking the 1st graded test just makes me insane, not because I don't know how to implement Encapsulation but due to the fact that it require you to do so many unrelated things
very useful for the new learner
